{"article_id":"CCu9QJbAPf0ZDbNF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Facebook founder and chief executive officer Mark Zuckerberg will strike an apologetic tone","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"when he appears before Congress this week ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"expressing contrition for the website ' s oversight of user data and its role in the 2016 election .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"In testimony at a joint hearing of the Senate Judiciary and Commerce committees on Tuesday and before a House committee on Wednesday , the famously aloof social media executive will take responsibility","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"for failing to handle its civic duties with more care .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"\" It ' s clear now","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that we didn ' t do enough","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"to prevent these tools from being used for harm ...","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"That goes for fake news , foreign interference in elections , and hate speech , as well as developers and data privacy , \"","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"he will say ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"according to advance testimony to the House Committee on Energy and Commerce released Monday .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" We didn ' t take a broad enough view of our responsibility ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and that was a big mistake .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"It was my mistake ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and I ' m sorry .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"I started Facebook ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"I run it ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and I ' m responsible for what happens here . \"","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"The hearings come","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"several weeks after it was reported","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that Cambridge Analytica , a data-mining firm","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"linked to President Donald Trump ' s 2016 presidential campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"had improperly stored the private information of tens of millions of users .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The Cambridge Analytica scandal is only the latest","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"to besiege the social media giant in the wake of the 2016 presidential election .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Last fall , a senior Facebook executive","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"( alongside representatives from Google and Twitter )","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"admitted before a congressional hearing","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that Russian actors had exploited advertising and networking social media tools","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to \" sow division and discord \" in the American political conversation both before and after the 2016 election .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Zuckerberg has since faced loud and widespread public criticism ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"while Facebook ' s stock has plunged .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"In his remarks before Congress , Zuckerberg is expected to explain the conditions","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"that allowed Cambridge Analytica to exploit private data","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"and detail how Facebook plans to prevent similar breaches in the future .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"In the written testimony","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"submitted ahead of Wednesday ' s House hearing ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Zuckerberg explained","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that in 2013 , a Cambridge University researcher launched a personality quiz on Facebook","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that drew on the personal information of the roughly 300,000 users","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"who installed it and millions more of their friends .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Zuckerberg stressed","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that it was only a year later , in 2014 , that the company revised its privacy policy","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to prevent Facebook applications from accessing this data ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"but by that point , the damage was done :","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"the researcher , Aleksandr Kogan , had already shared the lode of information with Cambridge Analytica .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"\" We have a responsibility","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to make sure","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"what happened with Kogan and Cambridge Analytica doesn ' t happen again , \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Zuckerberg writes in the testimony .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" We need to make sure","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that developers like Kogan","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"who got access to a lot of information in the past","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"can ' t get access to as much information going forward . \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"In the testimony , Zuckerberg articulates what those remedial strategies might look like .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"\" We ' re removing developers ' access to your data","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"if you haven ' t used their app in three months , \"","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he writes .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"\" We ' re reducing the data","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"you give an app","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"when you approve it","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"to only your name , profile photo , and email address .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"That ' s a lot less","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"than apps can get on any other major app platform . \"","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Get The Brief .","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"Sign up","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"to receive the top stories","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"you need to know right now .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Choose your country","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"United States of America","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"Afghanistan Albania","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"Algeria","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"American Samoa","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Andorra","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Angola Anguilla Antigua and Barbuda","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Argentina Armenia","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Aruba Australia Austria","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Azerbaijan Bahamas","depth":14},{"id":78,"tex